Lyrics:

Talk, talk, talk And it's breaking my heart (All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk) Shut up! Talk, talk, talk And it's breaking my heart (All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk) (Hey! Hey!) I don't need no other, please don't have to bother Tell me that you never tell the truth, boy All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk (oh, oh, oh) Talk, talk, talk And it's breaking my heart I listen to you run your mouth Every one else gather round Let me help you break it down (Oooh) Every time I hear you speak It's like a game of hide and seek Always lies, never truth Tell you what you're ought to do Ooh, I got your number down (oh oh) No need to put one over cause you're so fire, so fire You're all talk, sounds, words Don't believe a single word That I know you got for me   Blah blah blah are the words that you're saying I didn't wanna know, but now I know I can't go back Blah blah blah is the sound that I'm hearing Blah, blah blah, blah (oh, woah) Shut up!   All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk (hey, hey) Running on your mouth and thinking I'm not onto you Talk, talk, talk, talk (hey, hey) Stop wasting up my time yeah, with your stupid lies (hey!) I don't need no other, please don't have to bother Tell me that you never tell the truth, boy All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk (oh, oh, oh) Talk, talk, talk And it's breaking my heart (Oh oh, oh oh) Now I don't wanna hear it I want you off my mind (Oh oh, oh oh) No, I don't really need this I need someone to believe in   How bout you shut it, shut it up? Shut it up, shut it up? How bout you shut it, shut it up? Shut it up, shut it up? How bout you shut it, shut it up? Shut it up, shut it up? Blah, blah blah, blah (Yeah!)   All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk (hey, hey) Running on your mouth and thinking I'm not onto you Talk, talk, talk, talk (hey, hey) Stop wasting up my time yeah, with your stupid lies I don't need no other, please don't have to bother Tell me that you never tell the truth, boy All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk (oh, oh, oh) Talk, talk, talk And it's breaking my heart Running it up, running it up, your mouth (Talk, talk, talk, talk, hey! hey!) Running it up, running it up, your mouth (Talk, talk, talk, talk, hey! hey!) Running it up, running it up, your mouth (Yeah) All you do is talk, talk, talk, talk   Talk, talk, talk And it's (breaking my heart)
